<h3 class="bold">Video Example(s):</h3>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-featured">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="u9yp7a" data-video-descrip="Dark Fawful summons a group of dark energy spheres orbiting around himself and Bowser has to punch goombas through them at him or he will launch them at Bowser and do a lot of damage." data-video-title="Dark Fawful energy spheres" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/u9yp7a_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/u9yp7a.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/OrbitingParticleShield" data-video-tropename="Orbiting Particle Shield" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="5.00" data-video-rating-count="1" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/MarioAndLuigiBowsersInsideStory" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link featured-widget-vid">
